      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad aisgahje Josuüs/ un wifs Israëls ar winnu no Libnas lihds Lahkiſam/ un apmet-tahs prett winnu/ un karroja prett winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS node-we Lahkitu Israëta Rohkâ/ un wiꞥſch uhsjehme to ohtrâ Deenâ/ un kawe to ar Sohbina Afmini/ ar wiffahm Dwehfelehin/ kas eekſch ta btja/ pehz wiſſu/ ko wiꞥſch Libnai bij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs Orams/ tas Kehninsch no Geseras us angschu Lahkitam par Paligu/ bet Josuüs kawe to/ un winna Landis/ lihds ka wiꞥſch ne weenu no teem atlizzinaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Josuüs aisgahje/ un wifs Israëls ar winnu no Lahkiſa us Eglonu/ un apmettahs prett winnu/ un karroja prett winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un uhsnehme winnu tai paſchâ Deenâ/ un kawe to ar Sohbina Afmini/ un wiſ-fas Dwehfeles/ kas eekſch ta bija/ isdeldeja wiꞥſch tai Deenâ/ pehz wiſſu/ ka wiꞥſch Lahkitam bij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs Josuüs us angschu/ un wifs Israëls ar win-nu no Eglona lihds Eebroxam/ karroja prett winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un uhsjehme winnu/ ir-kawe winnu ar Sohbina Afmini/ lihds ar winna Kehnins/ u-ar wiſſu Pilssahfu/ un ar wi-fahm Dwehfelehin/ kas eekſch ta-btja/ wiꞥſch ne atlizzinaja ne we-nu pahri/ pehz wiſſu/ ko wiſ-fus Eglonam bij darrijs/ un isdelde-ja to ar wiffahm Dwehfelehim-kas eekſch ta btja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atgreeſahs Josuüs un wifs Israëls ar winnu uh-Debiru/ un karroja prett winnu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un uhsnehme winnu/ u-winnu Kehninu/ un wiffus win-na Pilssahfu/ un kawe tohs a-Sohbina Afmini/ un isdeldej-wiſſas Dwehfeles/ kas eekſch ta-btja/ wiꞥſch ne atlizzinaja n-weenu pahri/ ittin ka wiꞥſch Ge-bronam bij darrijs/ ta darrijs wiꞥſch Debiram un winna Keh-ninam/ un ittin ka wiꞥſch Libna-un winnas Kehninam bij darrijs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta apkawe Josuüs wiſ-to Setmmi Kalnôs/ un kas pret-Deenas-Widdu icr/ un tahs E-leijas/ un tahs Uppeinas Sem-mes/ ar wiſſeem winno Kehn-neem/ wiꞥſch ne atlizzinaja n-weenu pahri/ un wiꞥſch isdel-deja wiſſu/ kam Dwaſcha bija itt ka pawehlejis bij tas KUNgs-tas Israëta Deeivs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Josuüs kawe tohs n-Kahdes-Barneas lihds Gasai/ar-ridsan wiſſu Gosena Semini-lihds Gibeonam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Josuüs uhsnehme wi-fus fchohs Kehnins/ un wiſ-\n"
    }
  ],
